  "body": "## 📝 更新日志\n## [v3.0.18]\n\n### 功能更新\n\n- 添加图片自动超分功能（实验性，可能不稳定）\n\n### 优化\n\n- 阅读界面章节选择对话框定位到当前章节并高亮的功能 by @Enigma-Soul in https://github.com/deretame/Breeze/pull/135\n\n#### New Contributors\n\n- @Enigma-Soul made their first contribution in https://github.com/deretame/Breeze/pull/135\n\n---\n\n### 📦 推荐下载\n| 平台 | 下载链接 |\n| :--- | :--- |\n| **Windows** | [windows-installer-v3.0.18.exe](https://github.com/deretame/Breeze/releases/download/v3.0.18/windows-installer-v3.0.18.exe) |\n| **macOS** | [Breeze-macOS-v3.0.18.dmg](https://github.com/deretame/Breeze/releases/download/v3.0.18/Breeze-macOS-v3.0.18.dmg) |\n| **Android** | [app-arm64-v8a-release-v3.0.18.apk](https://github.com/deretame/Breeze/releases/download/v3.0.18/app-arm64-v8a-release-v3.0.18.apk) |\n| **iOS** | [Breeze-iOS-v3.0.18.ipa](https://github.com/deretame/Breeze/releases/download/v3.0.18/Breeze-iOS-v3.0.18.ipa) |\n| **Linux** | [breeze-v3.0.18.flatpak](https://github.com/deretame/Breeze/releases/download/v3.0.18/breeze-v3.0.18.flatpak) |\n\n> 💡 **不知道该下载哪个文件？**\n> 请查看 [详细安装指南](https://github.com/deretame/Breeze#-%E5%A6%82%E4%BD%95%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85)。\n",
